info.title: Callcredit.Insolvencies.Service Mastered Data
info.description: Adds resources in the Callcredit.Insolvencies.Service domain to the overall Callcredit Api.

get.summary: Retrieves a paged collection of all Disputes for a Insolvency record.records
get.description:
Available Query Strings :::
            'page' - The page query string is used to select the page index of results to view. For example: ...?page=5

parameters.name: insolvencyOrderId
parameters.description: The unique business key of the insolvency.

200.description: Request fulfilled. The message body contains the page collection of resources.

204.description: No information to send back. The HTTP header will not be returned and message body will be empty.

400.description: Bad request. The message body will contain details for the validation error that occurred.

401.description: Unauthorized. The message body will contain details for the authentication error that occurred.

403.description: Forbidden. The message body will contain error details indicating that the client is not authorised to perform the operation.

404.description: Not Found. The message body will contain error details indicating that the resource was not found.

405.description: Not allowed. The message body will contain error details indicating that the resource does not support verb.

parameters.name: disputeId
